   "source": [
    "# NEU Baselines Training — Colab\n",
    "\n",
    "Trains three baselines on FineWeb at 150M scale:\n",
    "1. **Pure Transformer** — standard pre-norm causal transformer\n",
    "2. **Pure Mamba-2** — standard SSM stack, no attention\n",
    "3. **Fixed Hybrid** — Jamba-style interleaving (every 6th layer is attention)\n",
    "\n",
    "All trained on same data, same tokenizer, same token budget.\n",
    "This is the foundation for comparing against Neu's dynamic routing.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Runtime**: T4 GPU (~16GB) | **Training**: ~4-6 hours | **Scale**: 150M params"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
